{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[{"kind":"hero","image":"ic_theme_intro.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources.","type":"text"}]}],"chapter":"Go further with more ressources","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"title":"Going further with more resources"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"stepsSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"runtimePreview":null,"code":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","type":"step","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can get it at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"icon finder"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects.","type":"text"}]}],"runtimePreview":null,"code":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","type":"step","caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Go to the website and learn things at "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}]},{"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to discover how OUDS works.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","type":"step"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository.","type":"text"}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox"}]}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","type":"step"},{"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions","isActive":true},{"text":"!","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"}],"title":"More resources","contentSection":[{"mediaPosition":"trailing","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"contentAndMedia"}],"anchor":"More-resources"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-6-going-further","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"modules":[{"projects":[{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies","sections":[{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies#Import-the-Swift-Package-and-the-libraries","kind":"task"},{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies#Check-Your-Understanding","kind":"assessment"}]}],"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)\/Import-of-the-Swift-Package-and-choose-its-librairies"},{"projects":[{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme","sections":[{"kind":"task","reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme#Basic-structure-for-the-app"},{"kind":"assessment","reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme#Check-Your-Understanding"}]}],"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-O